%% Diagram: Write path for a new Pin - shard derived from the board ID, no lookup service
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant Cfg as Shard config (ZooKeeper)
    participant DB as MySQL master for shard 3429

    App->>App: shard_id = (board_id >> 46) & 0xFFFF -> 3429
    App->>Cfg: which host serves shard 3429?
    Cfg-->>App: MySQL007A
    App->>DB: INSERT INTO db03429.pins (data) VALUES ('<JSON>')
    DB-->>App: AUTO_INCREMENT local_id = 7075734
    App->>App: pin_id = (3429 << 46) | (1 << 36) | 7075734
    App->>DB: INSERT INTO db03429.board_has_pins (board_id, pin_id, sequence)
    DB-->>App: OK
